Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.99,0:00:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从窗口眺望夜空的话\N窓から空を見ていると
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.69,0:00:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以看到很厉害的东西\Nとっても　すごいものを　見たんだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.59,0:00:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大人们都笑者说\N大人は誰も笑いながら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.59,0:00:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我电视看太多了\Nテレビの見過ぎと言うけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.29,0:00:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我绝对绝对\N僕は　絶対に絶対に
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.99,0:00:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会说谎\N嘘なんか言ってない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.79,0:00:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不会用名为常识的眼镜\N常識と言う眼鏡で
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.19,0:00:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对我们的世界\N僕たちの世界は
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.59,0:00:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,进行窥视\Nのぞけやしないのさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.59,0:00:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忘记了梦想的\N夢を忘れた
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.59,0:01:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古老的地球人啊\N古い地球人よ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.59,0:01:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是动画 这不是动画\Nアニメじゃない　アニメじゃない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.83,0:01:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好奇妙的感觉\N不思議な気持ち
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.93,0:01:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是动画 这不是动画\Nアニメじゃない　アニメじゃない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.53,0:01:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是真的\N本当のことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.13,0:01:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是真的\N本当のことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.84,0:01:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從拉比安玫瑰來了一個叫做露·露卡的女孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.12,0:01:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真希望亞加瑪快點從香格里拉出去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.94,0:01:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再在殖民衛星上開洞可就不得了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.13,0:01:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,努力去打開艙口我還是太天真了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.84,0:01:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當老好人的少年可活不下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.73,0:01:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第八話 二度敲響鎮魂的鐘聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.15,0:02:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,安眠吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.74,0:02:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薩克的勇士們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.90,0:02:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們多吃ㄧ些水果吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.09,0:02:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,潘帕,你怎麼可以死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.08,0:02:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了\N敲響使靈魂安息的鐘聲吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.29,0:02:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不去整裝新型MS,辦什麼喪禮阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.32,0:02:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是在地球..什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.82,0:02:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不知道再地球\N死人都要辦喪禮的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.91,0:02:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道哈曼大人替大家\N作天堂衛星還不夠嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.22,0:02:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個計劃阿...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.91,0:02:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家希望有更溫暖的\N人與人之間的交流阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.55,0:03:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在亞加瑪想從另一邊的艙口離開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.46,0:03:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,潘帕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.84,0:03:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們都忘記哈曼大人的話了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.17,0:03:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等戰勝後再來憑弔死者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.00,0:03:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.70,0:03:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請等一下,馬士文大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.35,0:03:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喪禮到此結束\N到安多拉號準備出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.67,0:03:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是喪禮還沒結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.10,0:03:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是馬士文大人的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.11,0:03:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打敗亞加瑪\N才是對死者最好的安慰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.40,0:03:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼你們還不懂嗎?\N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.89,0:04:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,接到信號的話你會下來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.93,0:04:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.22,0:04:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.48,0:04:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是信號彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.39,0:04:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是是紅色的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.62,0:04:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們在做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.76,0:04:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是艙口打開的信號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.90,0:04:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艙口打開的信號是青色的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.74,0:04:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那紅色呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.79,0:04:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是收破爛業者的集合訊號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.54,0:04:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了遭了\N奇馬達被
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.13,0:04:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收破爛業者抓起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.29,0:04:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的嗎?在艙口前面的廣場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.54,0:04:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想做什麼?當然是去就馬奇達了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.98,0:04:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殖民地的人真是廢物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.50,0:04:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.69,0:04:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收破爛工會真的那麼粗暴嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.00,0:04:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,何止粗暴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.36,0:04:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,工會的傢伙掌握艙口的開關權
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.88,0:04:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拿這個來賺取暴利呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.28,0:04:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣你知道事情的嚴重吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.29,0:04:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡怎麼進來的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.04,0:05:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她要進來很簡單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.64,0:05:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,核戰機比MS小多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.42,0:05:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布拉杜艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.42,0:05:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度開動Z高達了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.36,0:05:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他怎麼擅自出動?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.79,0:05:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他還很氣憤艦長不在甲板
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.26,0:05:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快阻止他!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.05,0:05:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才不能\把香格里拉的命運交給其他人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.39,0:05:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等露卡探完情況回來吧\N捷度你現在去太早了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.47,0:05:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在我們破銅爛鐵工會\N必須團結奮發才可以!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.77,0:05:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人想為了外頭來的人\N打開艙門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.17,0:05:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,試問外面的船\N過去曾給我們帶來好處嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.08,0:05:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.78,0:05:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的MS被他們破壞...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.28,0:05:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?你的MS怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.52,0:05:52.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了修好它\N我可是徹夜趕工做的阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.42,0:05:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他會壞掉也是外頭的人弄的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.67,0:05:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我們不能置之不理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.03,0:06:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡,她手腳真快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.63,0:06:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有有人家產被他們奪走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.81,0:06:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不覺得可惡嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.74,0:06:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可原諒!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.62,0:06:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可原諒!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.72,0:06:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要吃嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.00,0:06:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,我是素食者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.56,0:06:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你再做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.68,0:06:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我什麼壞事也沒做阿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.23,0:06:39.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹什麼?\N捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.25,0:06:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你太沒用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.65,0:06:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手!很危險的!會爆炸的,會爆炸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.39,0:06:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不是炸彈吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.40,0:06:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是強力炸彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.40,0:06:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別亂摸,不然可能...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.11,0:07:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵死了,安靜點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.38,0:07:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,點燃那個信號彈\N亞加瑪就會飛起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.43,0:07:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是敵人!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.44,0:07:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艙口還沒打開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.28,0:07:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擴大破銅爛鐵堆\N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.65,0:07:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是Z高達,不會錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.93,0:07:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要轟炸那裏的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.68,0:07:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬士文大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.10,0:07:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想做出危害殖民地的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.19,0:07:32.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是那裏接近中心部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.22,0:07:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打一炮也不會損及殖民地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.31,0:07:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了死去的人們\N這是非做不可的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.01,0:07:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰爭必然會帶來死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.57,0:07:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,士兵們將為吉翁工國\N而捐軀成仁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.90,0:07:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你必要厚喪死去的人阿\馬士文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.99,0:07:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.84,0:08:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是,怎樣才最能安慰他們的在天之靈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.50,0:08:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.52,0:08:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還不懂嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.40,0:08:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是...是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.33,0:08:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是替他們報仇,馬士文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.67,0:08:17.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬士文,只是挖墳墓是不夠的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.12,0:08:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也是軍人,應該瞭解這點的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.23,0:08:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遵從哈曼大人的命令\N是我們唯一能做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.72,0:08:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下手,下手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.49,0:08:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道...立刻發炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.74,0:08:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要怕,戰鬥,起來戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.71,0:08:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,Z高達呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.27,0:08:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒辦法馬上出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.14,0:08:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要開核戰機了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.65,0:08:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇馬達就留給你救\N你有辦法嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.73,0:08:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要看不起人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.24,0:08:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛!\N小心點阿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.98,0:08:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.81,0:09:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,安多拉連我們都想幹掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.19,0:09:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你發什麼呆?敵人過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.29,0:09:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個不是亞加瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.50,0:09:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說給你飯吃\N要你的工作的人就是你阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.45,0:09:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,男兒大志是不可輕易更改的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.58,0:09:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你...你支持亞加瑪嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.55,0:09:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒有死?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.70,0:09:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.31,0:09:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞加瑪在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.38,0:09:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那邊..那邊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.92,0:09:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.12,0:09:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快坐上MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.67,0:09:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.46,0:09:36.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快上來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.21,0:09:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要駕駛Z高達回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.56,0:09:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了,信號彈還沒拿回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.03,0:09:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那東西不重要!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.51,0:09:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞加瑪市看信號彈行動的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.70,0:09:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了,你等一下!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.67,0:09:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.38,0:09:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要打死他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.74,0:09:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到了,就是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.44,0:09:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.30,0:10:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才不會輕易被踩死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.08,0:10:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接著!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.80,0:10:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.18,0:10:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來吧...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.22,0:10:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.72,0:10:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新武器嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.33,0:10:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.33,0:10:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞加瑪行動的話怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.71,0:10:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得趕快通知那是誤射的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.49,0:10:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,藍色的煙火\N是艙口打開的信號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.68,0:10:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!準備上升\N全體人員回到崗位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.39,0:10:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OK!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.75,0:10:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.97,0:10:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就負責到底\N打開艙口就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.76,0:10:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們想打開艙口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.77,0:10:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逸札,阻止他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.84,0:10:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼做?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.83,0:10:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你自己想啊!\N可惡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.11,0:10:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我進入艙口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.03,0:10:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能進入嗎!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.03,0:11:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.49,0:11:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別管小老鼠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.35,0:11:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個小鬼跑去哪裏了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.11,0:11:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好了,被剛才的炮彈給埋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.40,0:11:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那艘船太過分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.83,0:11:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望駕駛艙安然無恙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.77,0:11:25.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小子,剛才你居然...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.42,0:11:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看後面!看後面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.89,0:11:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雅加瑪飛出來了,在右側地區
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.66,0:11:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了!糟了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.58,0:11:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出來的太早了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.45,0:12:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雅加瑪...原來是躲在那裏啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.42,0:12:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道有沒有問題?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.65,0:12:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼問題?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.79,0:12:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是哥哥沒回來怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.65,0:12:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.24,0:12:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度不是那種拋棄妹妹的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.89,0:12:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還比較擔心花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.56,0:12:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她想留在香格里拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.83,0:12:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卻勉強自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.94,0:12:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.89,0:12:34.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能源箱放自這裏阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.73,0:12:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝!剩下怎辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.82,0:12:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經全部放好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.11,0:12:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,我們來大展身手\N把敵人打的落花流水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.26,0:12:43.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對,這樣嘉美尤才...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.58,0:12:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看,客人登場了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.19,0:12:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很好,繼續追逐雅加瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.81,0:12:58.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是艙口打開的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.08,0:13:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時就發射主炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.32,0:13:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打開艙口就不會危害到市民\N正合我意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.16,0:13:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太花時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.37,0:13:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能動嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.40,0:13:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我趕上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.68,0:13:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也很沒用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.89,0:13:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少囉唆!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.33,0:13:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他想毀滅雅加瑪嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.39,0:13:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雅加瑪是很值錢的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.55,0:13:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Z高達?艙口打開了,他幹什麼回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.92,0:13:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下的拜託你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.11,0:13:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾莉!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.17,0:13:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,180度回轉,向艙口前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.57,0:13:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長!是捷度,他有話要說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.73,0:14:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.64,0:14:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才的信號是錯誤的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.38,0:14:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.33,0:14:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是誤射的煙火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.92,0:14:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你休想礙事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.82,0:14:13.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓雅加瑪出去就不值錢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.39,0:14:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停止回轉!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.43,0:14:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.96,0:14:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,引開敵人上升吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.73,0:14:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你再幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.25,0:14:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度在前面,我不能開炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.32,0:14:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.44,0:14:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起,我馬上趕走敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.55,0:14:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雅加瑪停止改變方向了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.72,0:14:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.78,0:14:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收破爛的MS妨礙雅加瑪的航行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.42,0:14:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是機會,開炮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.73,0:14:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼開炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.99,0:14:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會幫你調整光波威力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.51,0:15:02.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,萬一在殖民地上面開動\N我可不管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.71,0:15:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蓋特!你可別死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.48,0:15:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Z高達\N太好了,命中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.77,0:15:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾莉!你是何時...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.92,0:15:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特雷斯,準備主炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.48,0:15:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必要時可能會用上\N好好牽制安多啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.03,0:15:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.08,0:15:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼震動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.84,0:15:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你總是壞我的好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.27,0:15:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,肚子餓就更火大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.18,0:15:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有辦法你就開槍你就開吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.91,0:15:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放手阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.54,0:15:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Z高達,又是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.79,0:15:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你總是妨礙我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.32,0:15:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?這傢伙的身體...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.52,0:16:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我這個泰坦軍人得過悲慘生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.38,0:16:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被迫在垃圾堆工作\N拍那老頭的馬屁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.13,0:16:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全部都是你害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.89,0:16:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來這殖民地也是因為上次戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.37,0:16:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被你打敗才這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.50,0:16:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是我幹的\N你還裝傻!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.89,0:16:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你害我好幾次差點死掉!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.99,0:16:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說過不是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.99,0:16:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是我幹的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.62,0:16:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡緊急連絡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.30,0:16:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度告訴我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.63,0:16:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艙口打開了\N我說艙口打開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.26,0:16:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,詳情以後再說\N總之艙口打開了,快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.27,0:16:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.41,0:16:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下的拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.53,0:16:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡...好各堅強的女孩阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.68,0:16:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開始回轉!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.50,0:16:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你別做傻事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.67,0:16:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傻事?什麼意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.34,0:16:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回轉完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.06,0:16:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,前進\N不,後退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.05,0:17:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雅加瑪往艙口去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.21,0:17:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.88,0:17:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在攻擊會危害到殖民地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.24,0:17:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等他們開到不會波及到\N殖民地的地方在開炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.46,0:17:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙想撞上雅加瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.34,0:17:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雅加瑪,快逃,我也要逃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.04,0:17:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陸卡打開艙口了!\N你要逃到哪裏去?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.29,0:17:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.51,0:17:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,休想逃!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.98,0:17:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.04,0:17:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.57,0:17:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個是必殺變身術!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.21,0:17:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還差一點點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.01,0:17:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,開炮!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.82,0:17:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前面有MS的影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.36,0:17:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起幹掉發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.65,0:18:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,射激光炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.83,0:18:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.87,0:18:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,主炮被...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.70,0:18:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,安多拉依然接近中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.87,0:18:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們想在我們進入艙口攻擊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.81,0:18:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把主炮瞄準安多啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.14,0:18:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.45,0:18:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,計算距離,把安多拉擊沉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.08,0:18:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,主炮能源調整
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.32,0:18:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Z高達,你再幹什麼\N讓開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.62,0:18:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡!必須變為MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.67,0:18:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是Z高達!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.67,0:18:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我用哈瑪哈瑪出擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.34,0:18:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.40,0:18:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不然對不起死去的同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.63,0:18:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈瑪哈媽不能出擊嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.44,0:18:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.12,0:18:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.81,0:19:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發射甲板受到嚴重損傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.79,0:19:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.78,0:19:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈瑪哈瑪好還沒組合好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.46,0:19:12.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.53,0:19:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,安多拉飛離亞加碼的射程距離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.86,0:19:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無法控制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.50,0:19:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣下去...\N會對不起死去的同志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.38,0:19:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼大人說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.70,0:19:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必定要厚喪戰死的同志們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.72,0:19:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及在戰爭死去的殖民地的人民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.94,0:19:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.16,0:19:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是...我是新人類!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.93,0:19:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停下來變形吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.95,0:20:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ㄟ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.30,0:20:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.91,0:20:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.71,0:20:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.01,0:20:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.48,0:20:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.42,0:20:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擔心死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.74,0:20:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.75,0:20:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹的好,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.94,0:20:25.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒什麼了不起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.19,0:20:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就知道你會打贏,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.83,0:20:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.49,0:20:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她會引導亞加瑪去拉比安羅茲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.32,0:20:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要直接飛去宇宙?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.17,0:20:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不能破壞香格里拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.67,0:20:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還要工作還要上學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.93,0:20:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在亞加瑪學習一下比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.97,0:20:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不這麼認為嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.95,0:20:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長,要離開殖民地了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.66,0:20:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.71,0:20:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.15,0:21:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加油阿,亞加碼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.07,0:21:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽著,馬士文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.13,0:21:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過去我教導你許多道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.12,0:21:23.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實最重要的是\N去適應地球風俗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.22,0:21:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,理解當地人與那裏的習慣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.14,0:21:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣才能掌握地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.20,0:21:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼大人\N我該怎麼做才能夠理解呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.29,0:21:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬士文大人\N這是撞上安多拉的MS中找到的骨頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.45,0:21:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有一根骨頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.24,0:21:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.66,0:21:48.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是豬骨頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.47,0:21:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放下去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.75,0:21:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殖民地的市民也該厚喪才是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.95,0:22:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬士文大人\N下次我們一定要替同伴報仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.30,0:22:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬士文大人! 馬士文大人!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.00,0:22:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.46,0:22:13.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到厚喪能這樣提高士氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.84,0:22:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來這就是哈曼大人說的道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.58,0:22:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定會替你們報仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.84,0:22:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且一定將地球掌握在手裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.85,0:22:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有要加快組合哈瑪哈瑪\N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.34,0:22:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看著吧,亞加瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.10,0:22:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在没有道路的荒野里\N道もない荒れた原野に
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.10,0:22:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,建造铁路真是一件辛苦差事\Nレールを作るのは苦しいことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.10,0:23:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是\Nだけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.50,0:23:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以不知晓远方\N遠い向こうも知らなくちゃいけない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.70,0:23:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我们的路现在才开始\N僕達は これからなんだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.80,0:23:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人们都说我们是“忘记了梦想的小孩子”\N“夢を忘れた子供達”と 人は言う
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.50,0:23:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊啊 时代正在哭泣\Nああー 時代が泣いている
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.81,0:23:48.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我以為只要到了廣闊的宇宙就沒問題了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.14,0:23:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 馬士文卻賭上了玫瑰花 真煩人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.36,0:23:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巨大的MS悍馬·悍馬 很可怕 看起來很強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.08,0:23:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果我卻忘記了光束步槍的彈夾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.05,0:24:03.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼這就是拚死的作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.24,0:24:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下回 高達ZZ 宇宙的捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.39,0:24:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以看到NEWTYPE的戰鬥場面！

